Package: hierviz
Title: Visualization Tools for Hierarchical Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Artemas", "Radik", , "artemas@college.harvard.edu", role = "cre")
Description: Tools for flattening hierarchical category data and creating
    visualizations like line charts and change tables. Supports nested category
    structures and provides functions for data transformation and analysis.
